gplayer

This is a minimalist media player intended to provide you with control
at your fingertips. It also aims to make mplayer users feel at home in
the few controls it provides.

It is built using GStreamer, and may also be interesting if you want
to find out how to do specific things with GStreamer.

Current controls:
    9/0          decrease/increase volume
                 caution, this can increase volume up to 5 times original volume
    left/right   seek backward/forward 10 seconds
    up/down      seek backward/forward 60 seconds
    page up/down seek backward/forward 10 minutes
    a            switch to the next audio track
    j            switch to the next subtitle track
    q            quit the player
